                  <additions>
                    <list>
                      <item xml:id = "a1">
                        <desc>Supplication to the Cross and the Blessed Virgin, with musical notation, with incipit
                          <foreign xml:lang = "gez">
                            ወካዕበ፡ ናስተብቁዖ፡ ለዕፀ፡ ቅዱስ፡ መስቀል፡...
                          </foreign>
                        </desc>
                        <note>On this controversial supplication, see ጌታቸው፡ ኃይሌ፥ ደቂቀ፡ እስጢፋኖስ፥ (Collegeville MN: HMML, 1996 EC) 36–41</note>
